phrases: I got called over by my crush.
Have you still not worked up the courage?
D-Do you have a crush on anyone or anything, Takase?
What is the correct answer in this situation?
But then I would be stealing her confession.
But it is not like I do not have a crush...
No, I did not mean that.
Just say so if you do.
What do you mean, Fine, then?
Was not there something you wanted to talk to me about?
L-Like I said, I wanted to know if you had a crush on anyone.
I will tell you, and then what?
It is not that I am done.
But I kind of missed my chance today.
All right, I am leaving, then.
Would you meet up with me tomorrow, too?
I guess I should do it.
But first, there is something I...
You will meet up with me?
I forgot what I was going to say.
I-I will tell you tomorrow that I like you.
Minagawa-san, the class rep, does not do her job.
Could you help me out a little, Minagawa-san?
Then why did you become the class rep?
Could you please not mess with me?
It is true that I like you, though.
Is that supposed to be a confession?
Will you go out with me?
But there are rumors that you hang out with lots of guys.
Besides, I have guy friends, but it is not like that.
Do you think I am lying?
You think I would sleep with anyone, do not you?
You are getting horny just imagining me having sex.
I knew it, you are just toying with me!
But these things are always really awkward.
That is why I cannot tell if you are serious or not.
Then will you give me an answer if I told you properly?
I do not know you that well.
I-I do not know anything about dating yet.
No more, we are done talking about this!
You have not given me an answer.
You are going to laugh at me again if I try to answer, are not you?
Did I make you hate me?
Yeah, specifically how flippant you are.
Seriously, can we not talk about this?
So you do not totally hate me.
The student council president saw me smoking.
You are not going to rat me out, are you?
Nope, I am not a monster.
I will let you off the hook just this once.
If you give me a kiss, that is.
There is something that is been on my mind, actually.
I have never been in love with a woman.
I just have a hard time finding interest in women.
I cannot figure out what is so fun about dating.
So you want to kiss someone to find out?
I will teach you how to kiss.
No, I know how to kiss.
Well, it is not like this is my first time.
I will kiss anyone for money.
Then how much would you sell your body for?
Why do you have that much?!
You have never actually prostituted yourself, have you?
Who do you think you are talking to?
That proves you have never actually sold yourself before.
I want you to value yourself more.
I am still asking for that kiss, though.
Do not forget our agreement about your smoking.
I think I can fall in love with you.
As long as you quit smoking.
Senpai, show me the stars again tonight.
I was going to confess to you, too.
How many hundreds of times has it been?
This is a bad habit of mine.
I make a joke of my feelings for him.
I want to tell him how I feel, for real this time.
First, I think it is important to set the mood.
Is it all right if I huddle up with you?
Yeah, stay out of my way.
Also, is it okay if I push you down?
This is our last time seeing the stars from here.
This is the last time seeing the stars with you, too.
I mean, we could see the stars together if we really tried, though.
Have you learned any of the stars yet?
That is the first one I taught you.
I would never forget a star that you taught me, Senpai.
You are the only member in this club next year.
I am glad my juniors love me.
Would you be glad if I really liked you?
I told him I like him without joking about it!
I wonder if Yukawa-senpai will appreciate it.
Did you think I was being serious?
I cannot tell him I like him anymore.
I told Senpai I like him so many times over the past two years we spent together.
I could never tell him I was serious.
I will never get to tell him I like him.
I do not want to cry in front of Senpai.
I do not want to worry him.
I do not want to make it awkward.
I want him to smile like he did before.
Do not cry, do not cry, do not cry...
I am tired of hearing you say you like me.
I want to hear it one more time before I go.
I will say it, if you will not.
